The paper presents a novel technique for wireless video streaming that focuses on optimizing power consumption. This involves redesigning and optimizing both the camera and wireless communication modules. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Augmented Reality (cs.AR), and Robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
